[Reunion (previously Ile Bourbon) is a French island with a
population of about 800 000 located in the Indian Ocean, east of
Madagascar, about 200 km (120 mi) southwest of Mauritius, the nearest
island. Administratively, Reunion is one of the overseas departments
of France. A map of the island can be accessed at:
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%C3%A9union.

It must be presumed that this autochthonous case was infected by
contact with a visitor from outside the island. - Mod.CP]

