A brother and sister died of measles, while 3 others were admitted
for treatment in Jiyanpur area of the district, officials said today
[Sun 15 May 2011].

The 2 3-year-old children died due to measles this morning [15 May
2011] in Gangepur Varzala village, family members said. Teams of
doctors have been rushed to the village, and they were trying to
ascertain the reason for the death, Chief Medical Officer BB Singh
said.

