Viewing the geographical extent of the global outbreak of measles
revealed by these reports, with case numbers ranging from one to 16
000, the WHO revised target of the year 2015 for the final eradication
of measles virus infection, notwithstanding the existence of a cheap
and secure vaccine, seems overly optimistic. - Mod.CP]
